[Sir Syed University] - **Admission Fee:** The Rs. 35,000 admission fee is strictly non-refundable.  
- **Semester Freezing:** Must be done within 15 days of the commencement of classes.  
- **Tuition Refunds:** Follow national HEC guidelines (100% refund in week 1, 50% refund in week 2, 0% refund thereafter). _(Sources: SSUET Fee Structure Document; SSUET Student Handbook)_  
